<div class="policy-page">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="policy-title">{{ policy.title }}</h1>
    {%- if policy.handle == 'privacy-policy' -%}

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2 class="policy-heading">Who We Are</h2>
      <p class="policy-para">LaLume Skincare is a Canadian skincare brand based in British Columbia. We operate the website lalume.ca and are responsible for the personal information you share with us when you make a purchase or sign up for our newsletter.</p>
      <p class="policy-para">Questions about this policy can be directed to <a href="mailto:Lalumecare@gmail.com">Lalumecare@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2 class="policy-heading">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="policy-para">When you place an order, we collect your name, shipping address, email address, phone number, and payment information. Payment details are processed securely by Shopify Payments and are never stored on our servers.</p>
      <p class="policy-para">When you subscribe to our newsletter, we collect your email address only. You can unsubscribe at any time by clicking the link at the bottom of any email we send.</p>
      <p class="policy-para">We also collect browsing data such as IP address, browser type, and pages visited through Shopify's analytics. This data is aggregated and cannot be used to identify you personally.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2 class="policy-heading">How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p class="policy-para">We use your information to fulfill your order, send shipping updates, and respond to customer service inquiries. If you have opted in, we may also send you product updates and skincare content by email.</p>
      <p class="policy-para">We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for their own marketing purposes. We share data only with service providers necessary to operate our store, including Shopify (our platform), Canada Post and USPS (shipping), and payment processors.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2 class="policy-heading">Data Retention</h2>
      <p class="policy-para">We retain your order information for as long as necessary to fulfill our legal and accounting obligations, typically 7 years. You may request deletion of your personal data at any time by emailing <a href="mailto:Lalumecare@gmail.com">Lalumecare@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2 class="policy-heading">Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="policy-para">Under Canadian privacy law (PIPEDA), you have the right to access, correct, or request deletion of the personal information we hold about you. To exercise any of these rights, email us at <a href="mailto:Lalumecare@gmail.com">Lalumecare@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2 class="policy-heading">Cookies</h2>
      <p class="policy-para">Our website uses cookies to keep items in your cart, remember your preferences, and measure site traffic through analytics. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, though some features of the site may not function correctly as a result.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section">
      <h2 class="policy-heading">Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="policy-para">We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. Continued use of our site after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the updated policy.</p>
    </div>

    {%- else -%}
    <div class="policy-section">
      {{ policy.body }}
    </div>
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>
</div>
